# v

welcome to v - essential tools for programming in python!

## installation

linux / macos (python3):

```sh
python3 -m pip install v
```

linux / macos (python2):

``` sh
python -m pip install v
```

windows:

``` sh
py -m pip install v
```

[full guide](https://github.com/dylanopen/v/blob/main/docs/installation.md)
